pre_text_caption_evidence: we participate in a medicare health support pilot program through green ribbon health , or grh , a joint- venture company with pfizer health solutions inc .
grh is designed to support medicare beneficiaries living with diabetes and/or congestive heart failure in central florida .
grh uses disease management initiatives including evidence-based clinical guidelines , personal self-directed change strategies , and personal nurses to help participants navigate the health system .
